# Forms

**Validation is server-side only** — Laravel Form Requests. No Zod, Yup, or react-hook-form.

## Prefer: `useForm` (feature CRUD)

Parent owns form state; sheet/dialog receives `form: InertiaFormProps<T>`.

```tsx
const form = useForm<BranchFormData>({ name: '', code: '', ... });

form.put(`/organization/branches/${branch.id}`, {
    preserveScroll: true,
    onSuccess: () => setIsSheetOpen(false),
});
```

Reference: `features/organization/branches/index.tsx` + `branch-form-sheet.tsx`

## Prefer: `<Form>` (auth / Fortify)

```tsx
import { store } from '@/routes/login';

<Form {...store.form()} resetOnSuccess={['password']}>
    {({ processing, errors }) => ( ... )}
</Form>
```

Reference: `pages/auth/login.tsx`

## Error display

- Inline: `{form.errors.name ? <div className="text-destructive text-sm">{form.errors.name}</div> : null}`
- Shared: `<InputError message={form.errors.name} />`
- Toast fallback: `firstValidationError(form.errors)` from `lib/first-validation-error.ts`
- Employee record tabs: `pages/organization/_lib/apply-record-form-errors.ts`

## Creatable master data

`useCreatableMasterData` + `CreatableSelect` — reference `components/ui/creatable-select.tsx`

Settings master-data sheets: `components/settings/master-data-form-sheet.tsx`

## Document / profile forms

- Upload: `pages/organization/_components/documents/upload-dialog.tsx`
- Edit/replace: `edit-document-dialog.tsx`, `replace-document-dialog.tsx`
- Pass `partialReloadKeys={['documents']}` or `['document']` for targeted Inertia reload

## Avoid

- Client-side schema validation libraries.
- Uncontrolled forms without Inertia `useForm`/`Form`.
- Manual success toasts on CRUD — server flash is handled by `components/http-exception-toasts.tsx`.

## Backend pairing

Every form maps to a Form Request in `app/Http/Requests/{Domain}/`:

- `StoreBranchRequest.php`, `UpdateBranchRequest.php`
- Shared rules in `Requests/.../Concerns/` traits
